  "title": "Ayasa: Shadows of Silence",
  "description": "Brave the shadows in 'Ayasa: Shadows of Silence'. Journey across six realms, solve thought-provoking puzzles, and engage with a narrative rich in horror and philosophy.",
  "longDescription": "<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# About this game\n<!--text-->\na platformer that blends quests, horror, and puzzles into a thrilling adventure. Navigate six lands corrupted by darkness and restore balance by uncovering the light left behind. With its rich atmosphere and unique gameplay, Ayasa challenges you to survive a world full of danger, mystery and wonder.\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# Story\n<!--text-->\nThe Inverted World was once a harmonious place where good and evil coexisted, maintained by Tas, the Absolute. But now, darkness threatens to engulf everything, and Ayasa must embark on a perilous journey through the devastated lands of Faith, Hope, Love, Greed, Indifference, and Betrayal. Only by finding the remnants of Tas’s light can Ayasa hope to restore balance and save the world from complete destruction.\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# Key Features\n<!--text-->\n- A Dark and Surreal World: Explore hauntingly beautiful lands with a mix of vibrant and oppressive visuals.\n\n- Light and Shadow Mechanics: Use light to reveal hidden paths and manipulate shadows to navigate treacherous environments.\n\n- Challenging Puzzles: Solve intricate puzzles that test your logic, timing and creativity to progress.\n\n- Unique Abilities: Unlock Ayasa’s powers to outwit enemies and uncover secrets throughout the Inverted World.\n\n- Immersive Atmosphere: Experience a deeply atmospheric journey with a blend of horror and surrealism.\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# Gameplay\n<!--text-->\nIn Ayasa, you will navigate treacherous lands using light and shadow to solve puzzles, evade enemies, and uncover hidden secrets. Each area offers unique challenges, combining platforming with exploration, keeping you on your toes as you progress.\n\nEmbark on this unforgettable adventure and uncover the mysteries of the Inverted World. Will you restore balance or be consumed by the darkness?\n\n<!--textBlock-->\n<!--title-->\n# Art Direction\n<!--text-->\nStep into a magical realm where every visual detail enchants. Influenced by Tim Burton, Hayao Miyazaki, Robert Sahakyants, Yervand Kochar, René Laloux, Zdzisław Beksiński, and Franciszek Starowieyski, our art direction blends dark fantasy with a minimalist color palette to evoke both terror and wonder. Our levels, alive and surreal, are more than mere settings; they are vibrant characters that tell tales of awe, fear, and reflection.\nWelcome to a universe where each lit screen opens a portal to a surreal, noir fantasy world. Explore symbolic lands that transform every moment into a profound visual and emotional experience.\n",
